                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="becoming_col">
                    <div class="becoming-content">
                        <p>As a Laurels Partner, you'll manage property sales from start to finish — from building your personal brand within your exclusive postcodes, to handing over the keys on completion day.</p>
                        <p>You'll deliver a 5-star service to every client, using our expert marketing team to showcase homes with standout photography and high-quality marketing that sets you apart. Establishing your name and brand in your local area takes dedication, and while it can take up to six months, put in the effort, do it right, and you'll establish yourself as the go-to agent in your area — the one everyone turns to.</p>
                        <p>Social media is one of the most effective ways to grow your brand — and that’s why every team member commits to posting at least three times a week. It’s not just about visibility; it’s about building trust and becoming a familiar name in your area. The goal is simple: when someone’s ready to sell, you’re the first person they think of.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="becoming-content">
                        <p>You will receive ongoing support, training and guidance from one of our dedicated directors here at Laurels. We have all training materials available at your fingertips, you will receive social media support as well as a sponsored ad which will help you grow your brand in your area.</p>
                        <p>You will be allocated your own protected postcodes to sell out of which means you will earn money from every sale that completes in your postcodes! We offer quarterly training days for the entire team and a centrally located office you can access whenever you need, you'll always have the support and space to grow.</p>
                        <p>Over the past 10 years of selling property, our culture has remained the same. Experience isn’t essential — what matters most to us is that you're passionate, hardworking, and committed to delivering outstanding service to our clients. That’s how we’ve grown, and it’s how we plan to exceed £5 billion in property sales over the next five years.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="becoming-content">
                        <p>It is easy to be an ‘ok’ estate agent. At Laurels, we do not just want to be ‘ok, we’re striving to be the best across London and the home counties. That means we look for people who are ambitious, driven, and ready to push themselves. If you're up for the challenge, the rewards are huge — and so is the opportunity to grow with us.</p>
                        <p>Most employed estate agents don’t stay in the industry for long — and it’s no surprise. The financial rewards often don’t justify the long hours and hard work. At Laurels, we do things differently. With 70% commission, ongoing support, and the chance to build your own brand in your local area (without competing with former colleagues), your hard work won’t just be sustainable — it’ll be seriously rewarding.</p>
                        <p>Being a Laurels Partner means you’re not only earning the majority share of commission on every deal — you’re also gaining the freedom to work around your personal life. You’re in control of your time, your schedule, and your success. Whether it’s school drop-offs, midday gym sessions, or simply having the flexibility to take a break when you need it, this role gives you the autonomy to build a career that fits your lifestyle. All while having the backing, support, and resources of a professional team behind you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
<?php endif; ?>

